                            <comment id="62109" author="bogl" created="Thu, 11 Jul 2013 14:35:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just for reference I believe the commit that introduced this compiler error was 10b256a65b8fd746ca7952b40d9026a957b171bc, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3101&quot; title=&quot;Interop 1.8.9&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;2.4 failure on test suite replay-single test_61d: cannot restart mgs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3101&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3101&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; mgs: deregister the mount for failed case&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
